[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> # Let's test different rounding strategies!
[?2004l[?2004h> # Strategy 1: Round amount_usd to 2 decimal places first, then fee_usd is calculated and rounded to 2 decimal places.
[?2004l[?2004h> # Strategy 2: Do not round amount_usd, but round fee_usd to 2 decimal places.
